snippet.title: Beetle Bunt Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Beetle Bunt is a puzzle game about a beetle that likes to flip things over.


Help Herc the beetle shove tablets under the light, revealing inscriptions on the other side. Beat challenging block rotation and block position puzzles while testing your platforming skills.


Beetle Bunt releases on December 25, 2020.
